<br>
Smiling at the beautiful young man who was to satisfy her craving she led him by the hand back to the finely furnished residence she had designated as her lair. It had not taken her long to accumulate such finery......it was easy to gather a few gifts from her prey whilst she toyed with them and Amaya only chose the ones who could afford it.<br>
<br>
Taking the man upstairs to her bedroom Amaya slipped seductively out of the red velvet dress that had complimented her hair so beautifully. The man couldn't believe his luck! She wasted no time but kissed him passionately and quickly got to work. As the man burned with passion he caught a glimpse of what it truly was that he had in his arms. But it was too late, he was hers, spellbound, locked eternally in pleasure and terror. At the height of his fufillment his soul was lost and he was forever damned.<br>
<br>
