. &quot;Hey, what the hell?!&quot;, he demanded, more than a little surprised. &quot;Hush&quot;, Victoria replied in a stragely eerie voice, &quot;look into my eyes.&quot; The man looked up and was instantly transfixed. He stood there helplessly as Victoria drained him and then found a convienent place to hide the body. She licked her lips, smiling slightly to herself as she left the park and returned to her home.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=8.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=8.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=8.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showNextMessage?topicID=8.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic&index=52><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.emailToFriend?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.threadControl?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.unsubscribeUnregistered